      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/slovakia-s-rating-cut-at-moody-s-on-fiscal-and-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将斯洛伐克的主权信用评分下调了一个等级，理由是担心体制挑战和政治风险。]]></description>
