      <title>美联储会议前，新兴货币连续第二周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/currencies-drop-as-china-disappointment-rattles-emerging-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员为美联储今年最后一次会议做准备，新兴市场货币连续第二周下跌，周五巴西雷亚尔领跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/currencies-drop-as-china-disappointment-rattles-emerging-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 12:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
